snippet.title: Tom Clancy's Ghost Recon Phantoms - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Formerly Ghost Recon Online, Ghost Recon Phantoms launches with a new identity, new features and worldwide distribution.

Follow Ghost Recon Phantoms at GameSpot.com!
http://www.gamespot.com/tom-clancys-ghost-recon-online/

Check out our review!
